PEOPLE 
Philip Jacobs has been promoted from vice president to senior vice 
president-sales in the boys and preschool toys division of Mattel Inc., 
Hawthorne. 
Ronald Kesselman has been promoted to senior vice president-marketing and 
product development, preschool toys. Bob Rao has been promoted to senior vice 
president-marketing and product development, boys toys. In the girls and 
activity toys division, Joseph A. Cristina has been named vice 
president-finance and administration. Ramon Fuentevilla has been named senior 
vice president-sales. 
